text: A library is a place to keep quiet while others read and work. Staff Alfreda was observed to be coughing non stop. It seems very serious as she could not stop coughing. Insensitive during Covid season. The ladies staff seem to be very inconsiderate with their loud booming voices, shouting across a quiet place.

Small quaint and quiet library next to a laboratory. Limited amount of seats for reading and working.

Good selection of books and some interesting exhibits.
Not bad.. it is nice and quiet...
